What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Recycled Packaging Materials Market?



Market Analysis and Insights

Recycled packaging materials market will grow at a rate of 3.00% for the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Growing consumer concerns for the protection of the environment from hazards is an essential factor driving the recycled packaging materials market.

Packaging is used widely across industries which includes pharmaceutical, food and beverages, agro chemicals, household chemicals, sports and cosmetics among others. An extreme large chunk of waste generated by these industries comprise of packaging materials and products. Recyclable packaging can help in reducing the waste produced due to packaging materials and recyclable packaging also helps in reducing operational cost thus improving efficiency and minimizing waste.

Increase in the retail sector and rapid installation of modern retail stores in the APEJ region is the major factor escalating the market growth, also increasing consumer preference for eco-friendly stamped products, rising government initiatives towards sustainable packaging, rising shift in consumer preferences towards recyclable and eco-friendly materials, increasing downsizing of packaging, rising breakthrough in new technologies, changing consumer lifestyle and increased awareness for eco-friendly tagged products are the major factors among others propelling the growth of recycled packaging materials market. Moreover, rising growth of the E-commerce industry, rising research and development activities in the market and rising technological advancements and modernization in the packaging industry will further create new opportunities for the recycled packaging materials market in the in the forecast period of 2021- 2028.

However, rising poor infrastructure facilities for recycling, increasing lack of awareness about the importance of sustainability in some emerging economies and increasing cost of recycling are the major factors among others restraining the market growth, while rising fluctuations in the prices of raw material prices will further challenge the growth of recycled packaging materials market.

